"WRT-391L Rev. UB" is silkscreened on the board.
The router has three antennas despite the lack of three RX/TX chains. Two (right and middle) appear to be used in a switched diversity configuration.
The power adapter included with the router is a '''Leader Electronics''' M12-4120100-A1.
